race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Handicap (Bm62)
race.comment: Hard to go past A DIVA (4) who brings the clear best form and profile into this. She's had three runs to date, a dominant winner on debut here before just finding one better her past couple. Drops in class for this, gets every chance from the gate and should prove too strong. RIGHTEOUS (2) resumes. He's a lightly raced 5yo who only managed one run last time in, running well behind a stakes class mare in She's A Hustler. Have to respect if fit enough. ARIA ELECTRA (7) broke through for a solid win when last seen at Bairnsdale. Harder here but can run well again. MARIOTA (3) was good fresh here over 141mm and will appreciate the rise in trip. Draws for every chance and can run well. NORWOODS (5) next best.
